phrases: Ships from Le Garite and De Metrio are exchanging fire.
One of De Metrio's ships has lost control and is falling into our atmosphere.
It is coming down near this ship.
Ships that have lost their subspace fields can go ahead and break formation!
Tell them to avoid returning fire as much as possible!
We are trying all channels, but they continue to maintain silence.
What is the meaning of this, Dizelmine?!
How could I even think of breaking my vow
and cease pursuit of my own path?
I had already decided that day to defeat him, and return the Polyhedron to its rightful form.
I will now fulfill my duty as king.

The government has just announced that hostilities have broken out
between De Metrio and Le Garite forces in orbit above Earth.
As a result of this fighting, a De Metrio ship has crash-landed on Earth.
Authorities are investigating the extent of the damage.
The government has called an emergency session
from both De Metrio and Le Garite...
What do you think is going to happen now?
Apparently, Le Garite has commenced simultaneous attacks throughout the entire Polyhedron.
What are you trying to do, Dizelmine?
You are going in Orca, are not you?
I am going to find out what happened.
If this is something your brother started...
We do not know that for sure, yet.
We will have to find out for sure, will not we?
After that, we will just wing it.
Lan, it is too risky going alone, so I will go with you.
What took you two so long!
Are you planning to head for Dizelmine's ship alone?!
Do not look at me like that.
At this rate, the entire Polyhedron will become embroiled in conflict.
I need to ask Dizelmine himself if that is his true intention.
You will be in charge of the fleet until I return.
A single Ovid has left the De Metrio flagship.
How predictable can that man get?
I will deal with him myself.
It is a courtesy I extend as king.
Simply telling you would not have convinced you, right?
Were you two going to leave me behind like the last time?
No, that was not our intention...
But this is between Le Garite and De Metrio...
That is where you are wrong!
Lan, you do not get it at all!
You and Muginami are my comrades!
If you are sad, I am sad.
If you are happy, then I am happy, too!
Does that make me sound creepy to you?
Besides, the three of us together vowed never to use our Vox for battle.
If we are going to break that vow,
the three of us have to break it together!
If the two of you were in trouble, I would do the same thing!
Would not you do the same, Lan?
You are going to fly, are not you?
I packed you lunches, in case you get hungry.
I told him this was not a picnic, but...
The three of you are the pretty faces that bring business to my shop.
Do not go getting yourselves hurt, now.
Come back safely, so I can see your happy faces again.
Orca, let us fly together once more.
I am counting on you, Hupo.
Are you serious about starting a war?!
Have I ever, even for a moment, stopped fighting to protect the Polyhedron?
As long as he is saying that he is doing this for the sake of Polyhedron...
Then I must trust him, more than anyone!
Regardless of how badly I want to kill this bastard!
A ship is emerging from warp up ahead!
Why are you being so shy right now?
Come on, I am willing to listen to what you want to do with the Polyhedron, just like old times!
Great, who is it this time?
That is some pretty sorry flying for the king of De Metrio.
Lax Lestorine Ha Kirius, here to assist in the name of honor.
Do not get the wrong idea.
I am only here to protect Kamogawa.
I do not want this ocean to meet the same fate as De Metrio.
We knew a battle had begun
when we first came out of warp.
That is when Kirius said we were heading back to Earth.
the captain of the spaceship to turn back.
I did not threaten him, I convinced him.
You convinced him by sticking a sword to his throat.
We will not get in the way of any direct talks
We will not allow anyone to destroy Kamogawa!
Feel the power of my swordsmanship
What is your next move, Dizelmine?
It is just the two of us now.
What do you say, let us be honest with each other?
Do not try to hide it.
What is he been telling you this time-?
Are you insinuating that he made me do this?
It was all my own decision!
I am getting a Vox reading that is not in our database!
Are you sure it is not a sensor error?
Are you saying there is another Vox aside from Yurikano's Core?
Do you realize what you have done?!
Do you really want to control this world so badly?!
I listened to your plan to achieve peace through talks.
But to me, your vision of the future holds nothing but flaws,
You intend to create the world by yourself?!
You need to listen to other opinions
I have no need of other opinions!
Especially not from the likes of you, who is only interested in personal gain!
Of course, nothing I say will convince you, when I look like this.
Hold on, this is between me and...
This is also our problem now.
It is not like you to do things this way!
You love peace more than anyone.
you wished happiness for the people of Le Garite and the Polyhedron!
Do not act like you know me!
The enemy Vox has crash-landed on Maebara Beach.
She went for an axe kick right off the bat...
That was a roundhouse kick to the head.
You have the nerve to attack your own sister?!
I thought you would made up with Big Brother Giuvi!
I thought you would vowed to work together!
I was not the one who betrayed the other first...
The people I despise more than anyone!
The ones who tried to destroy the peace of the Polyhedron,
That was a long time ago!
Why did you do it, Villagiulio?!
You, of all people, should have known!
The many sacrifices our ancestors had to make
to build the peace and stability that we have today!
That life is a miracle in itself!
Get me a damage report immediately!
What happened to Madoka and the others?
We are checking on them now.
At this point, all I care about is killing you!
Research institutes around the world are reporting changes in quantum particle levels!
The same thing that happened 20,000 years ago.
No, the entire universe will be...
If you plan on doing anything more...
On the water's surface I see a light reflected that stirs my heart
we were already deeply connected under the blue sky
We had so much fun, as in a daze, that time seemed forgotten
I prayed that there would be no end to the way we lived
I will not forget our days together, although time goes by,
and you are far from me now,
because you left behind a wonderful world
Could it be the nether world?
Madoka, could it be that we are inside the Rinne?
Betrayal over the skies of Kamogawa
